channel.title: [TrIcKzzCraft!] 1.7.9 | Mini-games | Looking for staffs! | Survival
channel.description:
[b]TrIcKzzCraft![/b]
Server contains the following:
[b]Arcade:[/b] Consists of lots of mini-games Such as Splegg/Paintball/Quake/HidenSeek
[b]Survival:[/b] Server in the server where you gather stuffs and items and fight some mobs to earn some money. It's like an economy server
[b]VIP Community:[/b] A place where "VIP to Higher rank" ranked players (Donate for VIP) will hang out. A place where they can chill out and relax for as long as they want to.
[b]TrIcKzzGames:[/b] This is the TrIcKzzCraft Official Hunger Games Server, This is a mini-game where you start getting an item from the chest in the middle and get some stuffs, gather and find some chests during your way escaping. until all of the players will fight to the death.
Thanks guys! This is one of the helpers in TrIcKzzCraft, RansuKakuro We'll see ya'll there! C:
TrIcKzzCraft Official Server IP Address: cedoutrickzz.mc-srv.com TrIcKzzCraft Official Server Website: trickzz.enjin.com[/b
[b]Server Video Trailer[/b Made by: HolyDoktor/OddDoktor (Server Admin) Sub him too! [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bFtYaPHwHzw[/youtube]
Almost forgot, Server is still looking for Staffs Make sure to apply in the TrIcKzzCraft website: Thanks again guys!
